posting_body: ['The Economist', '1578 Humboldt, Denver, CO, 80218', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 95', 'OR Text', '95', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to contact our leasing team.', 'Welcome to The Economist', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 263 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome home to the Economist.', 'This newly constructed building is chock full of incredible amenities in Denver’s Uptown neighborhood.', 'Think: in-unit laundry, the latest appliance fixtures, and even a rooftop deck.', 'With 1 beds and micro studio options, you’re able to choose the amount of space that best-fits your lifestyle and needs.', 'Not to mention, Uptown offers tons of great dining, entertainment, & nightlife options meaning you’ll never run out of new foods to eat & new places to explore.', 'Features', '- Quartz Countertops', '- Micro-Studio, Studio, and 1 Bedroom Options', '- Hardwood Style Floors in Select Homes', '- In-Home Washer/Dryer', '- Polished Concrete Flooring in Select Homes', '- Fiber Internet with Dish Network at Additional Cost', '- Designer Tile Backsplash and Custom Cabinetry', '- Air Conditioning', '- Stainless Steel Appliance Package', 'Community Amenities', '- On-Site Management', '- Reserved Parking Based on Availability', '- City & Mountain Views', '- Pet Friendly', '- Fitness Center', '- Rooftop Deck/Patio', '- Community Living Room', '- Controlled Access/Gated', '- Online Rent Payment and Resident App', '- Smoke-Free Building', '- 24 Hour Emergency Maintenance', '- Bike Storage', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:10:00AM-6:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Fees are as follows per pet up to a limit of 2:', 'Fee: $300', 'Deposit: $100', 'Monthly Pet Rent: $35', '8lu1WyJHQHj']
